@startuml
actor "Logistics Operator" as Operator
participant "Port Logistics System" as System

activate Operator
Operator -> System: Authenticate
activate System
System --> Operator: Authentication result
deactivate System

Operator -> System: Create staff member
activate System
System --> Operator: Confirmation of creation
deactivate System

Operator -> System: Filter staff members (to update)
activate System
System --> Operator: List of filtered members
deactivate System

Operator -> System: Update staff member data
activate System
System --> Operator: Confirmation of update
deactivate System

Operator -> System: Filter staff members (to deactivate)
activate System
System --> Operator: List of filtered members
deactivate System

Operator -> System: Deactivate staff member
activate System
System --> Operator: Confirmation of deactivation
deactivate System
@enduml
